spec_data.Name: python2-xlrd
spec_data.Description:
Extract data from Excel spreadsheets (.xls and .xlsx, versions 2.0 onwards)
on any platform.  Pure Python (2.6, 2.7, 3.2+).  Strong support for Excel
dates.  Unicode-aware.
